description: nextractplus Server, VIOS and LPAR Performance stats including virtual resources v41

options.content:
# Python code and Graph Dashboard Notes
## Code Version 41
* Simplify parameted to a single .json file per HMC
* Watts, temperature and SSP share the same database
* Energy handles variable number of CPU & Planar stats
* Code reduction for speed and reliability
* New/improved Grafana dashboards
* Rework nextract articles
* Removed Clock

1. Graphs of all servers during the period (Computer room view)
2. Selected Whole Power Server data, Hypervisor & Shared Processor Pool (SPP)
3. Virtual I/O server (VIOS) with Network, Storage & Shared Storage Pool (SSP)
4. Virtual I/O Server (VIOS) virtual resoures - network (SEA, SRIOV) and storage vSCSI, vFC)
5. ALL LPARs of a Server showing busy LPARs: AIX, IBM i & Linux
6. Selected LPAR data CPU used, RAM allocated & Virtual I/O Client data
7. New and experimental graphs and HEA
